About

 

Hi. I'm Sanaa.

I'm a dynamic macOS developer, with great attention to detail and a passion for generating compelling user experiences. I'm currently working at Dashlane. I have a strong interest in the latest technologies and focuses on getting the Dashlane Mac application to the next level.

Prior to joining Dashlane, I spent an exciting year at Apple Inc. where I was working as a Language Technology Engineer and a Mac OSX developer intern within the Siri team in Cupertino.

I hold a software engineering degree from the University of Technology of Compiègne in France and a two-year degree in Mathematics and Computer Science from the University of Sciences of Rabat in Morocco. Also, I did an exchange program at the Polytechnic University of Valencia in Spain.

I enjoy traveling internationally and when I'm not working, you are likely to find me at the gym or spending time with friends and family!
